Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tears and doubts in tow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}onore no iro de egaite yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's paint it in our own colors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Yamato's Past!\NThe Man Who Came for an Emperor of the Sea!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--He went that way!\N--Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,BANQUET HALL, THIRD FLOOR, INSIDE THE CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When a man makes up his mind,\Ndon't try to hold him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's walking out on us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you tell me to wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fighting like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad boy... Don't try to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, gentleman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:08.37,OS,,0,0,0,,BLACK MARIA - A MEMBER OF THE TOBI ROPPO\NSPIDER-SPIDER FRUIT, ANCIENT TYPE\NROSAMYGALE GRAUVOGELI MODEL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here forever. You'll be my pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...I look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Women, women, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got to be out of his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute. As a reward for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna open heaven's door for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,FOURTH FLOOR, INSIDE THE CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get hurt if you \Ndon't get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:08.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,CAT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat went ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna give Kaido-{\i1}san{\i0} trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...bullying my subordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.54,OS,,0,0,0,,WHO'S-WHO - A MEMBER OF THE TOBI ROPPO\NCAT-CAT FRUIT, ANCIENT TYPE\NSAVER-TOOTHED TIGER MODEL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a former Warlord of the Sea,\N"First Son of the Sea" Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so childish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the helmsman of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you use that worthier title instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen you at one point\Nwhen you were a Warlord...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes people completely \Nchange their positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe I used to be on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? I wonder who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I take off your mask,\NI might be able to recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:40.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,FORBIDDEN STOREHOUSE, INSIDE THE DOME
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This brings me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...the memory of the wounds\Nthat I inflicted on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Inflicted wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you fought and beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't matter if I had won or lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the meaning of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was him, without a doubt, \Nwho taught me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The place they said children \Nwere being held...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...must be that island, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fight you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the Onigashima gate guards\Nwould be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What a letdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't lower your guard.\NOur enemy is that infamous Emperor of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No one's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido is the only one we need to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, go save the children while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--Got it!\N--Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?! State your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to take Kaido's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I found them! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared. We're here to save you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All the children are okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But our target, Kaido, \Nis nowhere to be found!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Father and the others went on an expedition.\NRight now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,not a single officer is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's Kaido's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we've had enough of this rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have time to wonder who I am,\Nget out of here now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring them back to their families!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it okay for you to let us go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no obligation to protect this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I hate seeing them\Nkidnapping such little children!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear what she said?\NIf Kaido isn't here, there's no point in us staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go back to the Land of Wano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your families are waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm indebted to you for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Nshow your families that you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure about it, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go back to the mainland without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, look after them.\NI'll catch up to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not convinced that such a strong person\Nisn't a captain or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll settle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was bored anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why aren't you going out to the sea\Nif you're so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to, but I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never be able to \Nunderstand my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I stay here\Nwithout going out to the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all his fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he's my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all your father's fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't choose your parents, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gol D. Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Gold Roger?\NDid you ask me if I know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize why there is so much destruction\Nin the world caused by pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all Roger's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that right before his execution,\Nhe bullshited about this great treasure thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...causing the idiot pirates who believed him\Nto run wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,--He should've never been born in the first place!\N--He was just a worthless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a nuisance - living or dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention the name that makes me sick, brat!\NIt's ruining my drink! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!\NYou little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ace?\NI heard that you're out of control these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--Old man.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I deserved to be born?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll see as you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...choose your parents, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You don't have to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he's my father,\NI don't have freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you cuffing me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're thinking about the wrong things.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even have one good reason to leave this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're my son, become stronger for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think about anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Uncuff me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been confined on this damn island
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and put in handcuffs\Nwhich will explode if I step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice\Nbut to stay here for my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because I was born\Nto that asshole named Kaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though handcuffs were unavoidable,\Nif you hate your father so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you letting them chain your heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you become stronger\Nto protect your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:15:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Or to let off some steam\Nby fighting someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You became stronger for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you really wanna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...deep, deep inside of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside of my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:49.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,ODEN'S TRAVEL RECORD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you really wanna do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even have one good reason\Nto leave this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was holding myself back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help dreaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't do as I wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosive handcuffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,An impossible dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll be stuck on this damn island."\N"I have no choice."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's all my father's fault."\NThat's what I was telling myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I now realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna sail out to the sea\Nand go on an adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna live freely like Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting off this crappy island...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna live freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--That's how it should be.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I ended up like this\Nwith someone who came to kill my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you love your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee! You keep attacking my soft point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,About you and your adventure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,About the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,About anything and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's gonna take a while,\Nso get ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,WISHFUL MOON\NSNOW MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And he came home in tatters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were young,\Nhe really caused me a lot of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--Your brother's so interesting!\N--Yeah, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how are things on the outside?!\NAre there many young people rising to fame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Young ones? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's talking about Caven-something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm in a class of my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but I heard some dangerous guys\Nare running wild in each sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid in the South Blue and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...Law in the north and Bege in the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But the toughest one\Nwill come out to the sea in a few years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be extremely powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times\Ndo you have to mention your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,--Who cares? Just listen!\N--Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,--You... That hurts!\N--Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awesome friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The truth is I'm the one\Nwho broke this dragon statue first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is a warning from me to Kaido\Nthat I'll come back again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not know there was a pirate\Nwho tried to save the Land of Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That made my father angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the end, he never met Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wait...\N--Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say Kaido is my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I hate him!\NI told you I'm Oden, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That confuses us even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be scared.\NI hate Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I dreamed of the sea and an adventure,\Nso I became Oden who lived freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand most of it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate your treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being so formal and come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, if you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yamato,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,where is the man\Nwho tried to save the Land of Wano now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace died two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Otama, you knew Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we were so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to become a {\i1}kunoichi{\i0}\Nbelieving in Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but Big Bro Luffy insensitively said...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it to me out of the blue\Nand it made me so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. That's what he's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But Otama, Luffy's been \Nthrough a lot of pain, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--When that happened...\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't do anything \Nat that time, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy lost Ace right in front of his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. He is no longer in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was waiting for his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:23:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...Straw Hat Luffy who inherited Ace's will,\NI can...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zoro and Marco work together\Nto face the Lead Performer's fierce attacks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To the top of the pirate world with Luffy!\NWith that unwavering belief, Zoro charges.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Marco sees in his bravery\Nthe image of the comrade he swore allegiance to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if he'll never see him, \Ntheir bond will last forever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Marco's Tears! The Bond of the Whitebeard Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.36,0:23:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:49.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,
